<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<title>Xiao555 | Login</title>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css" />
		<script type="text/javascript" src="js/jquery-1.12.3.min.js" ></script>
		<style type="text/css">
			.footer {
				position: relative;
			}
			html {
				overflow-y:scroll;
			}
			header {
				position: fixed;
			}
			th ,td{
				padding: 3px 5px;
			}
			.main {
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				position: relative;
				background-color: rgba(90,67,124,.9); 

			}

			.main:after{
				content: ".";
			    display: block;
			    clear: both;
			    visibility: hidden;
			    line-height: 0;
			    height: 0;
			}

			.main-content {
				position: relative;
				width: 80%;
				top: 10px;
				left: 50%;
				transform: translateX(-50%);
				text-align: center;
				height: 60%;
			}
			.main-content table {
				width: 100%;
				overflow-y:scroll;
			}

			.main-content .update {
				text-decoration: none;
				background-color: transparent;
				-webkit-text-decoration-skip: objects;
				color: #fff;
				background-color: blue;
				opacity: .8;
				padding: 3px 5px;
				border-radius: 4px;
			}

			.del {
				background-color: red;
				border: 1px solid red;
				cursor: pointer;
				opacity: .8;
				color: #fff;
				border-radius: 4px;
			}

			.upload {
				display: block;
				position: relative;
				width: 20%;
				left: 85%;
				transform: translateX(-50%);
				background-color: transparent;
				text-align: center;
				border: 3px solid #fff;
				line-height: 1em;
				padding: 1em 1em;
				color: #fff;
				transition: transform .2s ease-in, background-color .2s ease-in;
				cursor: pointer;
			}
			input[type='submit'] {
				position: absolute;
				top: 20px;
				right: .1%;
				display: inline-block;
				background-color: transparent;
				text-align: center;
				transform: translateX(-50%);
				border: 3px solid #fff;
				line-height: 1em;
				padding: 1em 1em;
				color: #fff;
				transition: transform .2s ease-in, background-color .2s ease-in;
				cursor: pointer;
			}
			input[type='submit']:hover {
				background-color: rgba(0,0,0,.1);		
			}
			.msg{
				width: 100%;
				text-align: center;
				margin-top: 10px;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<header class="intro">
			<div class="intro-fixed">
				
				<div class="row">
					<svg version="1.1" id="svg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" x="80px" y="0px" viewBox="50 0 250 400" width="250px" height="400px" xml:space="preserve">
					<!-- face -->
					<path class="svg-no" d="
					M150 80 H200 L250 100 L270 150 L250 300 L200 320 H150 L100 300 L80 150 L100 100 L150 80 Z
					" style="stroke:#fff;stroke-width: 5;"></path>					
					<!-- hair -->
					<path fill="#fff" d="M100 100 L140 150 L140 130 L190 160 L185 135 L240 155 L220 120 L270 150 L250 100 L200 80 L150 80Z" style="stroke:#fff;stroke-width: 5;"></path>
					<!-- ear-->
					<path class="svg-no" d="
					M85 190 H66 V240 L93 250 Z
					" style="stroke:#fff;stroke-width: 5;"></path>
					<path class="svg-no" d="
					M265 190 H284 V240 L257 250 Z
					" style="stroke:#fff;stroke-width: 5;"></path>					
					<!-- eyebrow -->
					<path class="svg-no left-eyebrow" d="
					M120 170 H150 Z
					" style="stroke:#fff;stroke-width: 5;"></path>
					<path class="right-eyebrow" class="svg-no" d="
					M200 170 H230 Z
					" style="stroke:#fff;stroke-width: 5;"></path>
					<!-- eyes -->
					<circle class="left-eye" cx="135" cy="200" r="10" fill="#fff"></circle>
					<circle class="right-eye" cx="215" cy="200" r="10" fill="#fff"></circle>
					<!-- nose -->
					<path d="M160 240 H190" style="stroke:#fff;stroke-width: 5;"></path>			
					<!-- MOUSE -->
					<path d="M150 290 L200 285 Z" style="stroke:#fff;stroke-width: 5;"></path>					
					<!-- SHOULDERS -->
					<path d="M135 330 L50 350"  style="stroke:#fff;stroke-width: 5;"></path>
					<path d="M215 330 L300 350"  style="stroke:#fff;stroke-width: 5;"></path>
					<path class="svg-no" d="M120 335 
					C 200 390 200 390 230 335
					"  style="stroke:#fff;stroke-width: 5;"></path>
					<!-- neck -->
					<path class="svg-no" d="M130 310 L140 350" style="stroke:#fff;stroke-width: 5;"></path>
					<path class="svg-no" d="M220 310 L210 350" style="stroke:#fff;stroke-width: 5;"></path>
					</svg>
					<article class="head-article">
						<h1>Xiao555</h1>
						<h2>A SOPHOMORE STUDENT IN XIDIAN UNIVERSITY</h2>
						<p>我是一个前端开发者,现在正在努力学好它.我选择它的原因是我认为他是技术与艺术的结合.</p>
						<p>除了前端之外,我还喜欢打篮球,会画充满灵气的山水画,喜欢摄影，有自己的一台佳能700D,虽然是入门级的,但是我希望能用它记录生活的点滴.</p>
						<a class="button" href="mailto:zhangruiwu32@gmail.com">
							<span>Let's Talk</span>
						</a>
					</article>
				</div>
			</div>
		</header>
		<main class="main">
			<div class="main-content">
				<a href="/upload" class="upload">上传</a>
				<table>
					<tr>
						<th>标题</th>
						<th>创建时间</th>
						<th>更新时间</th>
						<th>更新</th>
						<th>删除</th>
					</tr>
					<% for(var i=0;i < blogs.length;i++){ %>
					<tr class="item-title-<%=blogs[i].title %>">
						<td><%=blogs[i].title %></td>
						<td><%=blogs[i].time %></td>
						<td><%=blogs[i].updatetime %></td>
						<td><a class="update" href="/admin/update/<%=blogs[i].title %>">更新</a></td>
						<td><button class="del" type="button" data-title="<%=blogs[i].title %>">删除</button></td>
					</tr>
					<% } %>
				</table>
			</div>
			
		</main>
		<footer class="footer" role="contentinfo">
			<svg class="svg-angle" viewBox="0 0 50 50" preserveAspectRatio="none">
				<polygon points="50,0 0,50 50,50" fill="inherit"></polygon>
			</svg>
			<nav class="footer-nav">
				<a id="toHome" href="../">Back To Home</a>
			</nav>
			<small class="text-center">
				@Xiao555 2016
			</small>
		</footer>
		<script type="text/javascript" src="js/velocity.js" ></script>
		<script type="text/javascript" src="js/login.js" ></script>
		<script type="text/javascript" src="js/admin.js"></script>
	</body>
</html>